Nyandarua Governor Francis Kimemia on Monday congratulated President Uhuru Kenyatta following the decision by the Supreme Court to uphold his re-election on October 26.
 According to Mr Kimemia, the decision by the court was a clear confirmation that Kenyans will never again fight over political competition. 
